title: Quick Take: Donald Trump Wins Nevada
description: That's three primary state victories in a row for Donald Trump. Political editor Domenico Montanaro and campaign reporter Sam Sanders discuss his win and what's next on the GOP side of the race. Find them on Twitter @DomenicoNPR and @samsanders, or email the show at nprpolitics@npr.org.
